{
  "uid": "otel-pipeline",
  "title": "TrustUsBank — OTel Pipeline (end-to-end)",
  "tags": ["trustusbank", "otel", "tracing"],
  "schemaVersion": 39,
  "version": 3,
  "refresh": "30s",
  "time": { "from": "now-30m", "to": "now" },
  "panels": [
    {
      "type": "text",
      "title": "How OTel flows in this cluster",
      "gridPos": { "h": 6, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 0 },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "**Pipeline**: kagent agents + MCP servers + agentgateway → OTLP gRPC :4317 → otel-collector → **Tempo** (traces) + **Loki** (logs). agentgateway samples 100% (`manifests/phase05-agentgateway/tracing.yaml`).\n\n**What this dashboard proves (top to bottom):**\n\n* **Top stats**: `agentgateway_mcp_requests_total{method=\"tools/call\"}` proves the gateway is scraped by Prom (PodMonitor in `manifests/phase02-observability/agentgateway-podmonitor.yaml`). A2A is counted from kagent pod logs because A2A doesn't transit agentgateway in this setup — the chatbot calls kagent directly.\n* **Rates**: per-MCP-server tool-call rate (Prom); per-pod log rate (Loki).\n* **Traces**: agentgateway emits a span per MCP hop; each MCP server emits a span per tool call. *Direct agent-reasoning spans (`support-bot`, `fraud-bot`, `triage-bot`) are not currently in Tempo* — kagent isn't wired to the OTel SDK for its own work; that's a separate gap.\n* **Logs**: MCP stdout + ztunnel access lines for the same window — use these to correlate a request with the trace and the mesh's verdict."
      }
    },

    {
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Tool calls / min (agentgateway)",
      "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 8, "x": 0, "y": 6 },
      "targets": [
        { "expr": "sum(rate(agentgateway_mcp_requests_total{method=\"tools/call\"}[5m])) * 60", "refId": "A" }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "A2A calls / min (inbound POSTs on agent pods)",
      "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 8, "x": 8, "y": 6 },
      "datasource": { "type": "loki", "uid": "loki" },
      "targets": [
        { "expr": "sum(count_over_time({namespace=\"trustusbank-bank-agents\"} |~ `\"POST / HTTP` [5m])) / 5", "refId": "A" }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "MCP-server log lines (5m)",
      "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 8, "x": 16, "y": 6 },
      "datasource": { "type": "loki", "uid": "loki" },
      "targets": [
        { "expr": "sum(count_over_time({namespace=\"trustusbank-bank-mcp\"}[5m]))", "refId": "A" }
      ]
    },

    {
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Tool calls / sec by MCP server + tool (Prom)",
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 10 },
      "targets": [
        { "expr": "sum by (server, resource) (rate(agentgateway_mcp_requests_total{method=\"tools/call\"}[1m]))", "refId": "A", "legendFormat": "{{server}}.{{resource}}" }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "MCP-server log rate by pod (lines / sec)",
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 10 },
      "datasource": { "type": "loki", "uid": "loki" },
      "targets": [
        { "expr": "sum by (pod) (rate({namespace=\"trustusbank-bank-mcp\"}[1m]))", "refId": "A", "legendFormat": "{{pod}}" }
      ]
    },

    {
      "type": "table",
      "title": "Recent agentgateway hops (Tempo — proxies every MCP/A2A call)",
      "gridPos": { "h": 10, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 18 },
      "datasource": { "type": "tempo", "uid": "tempo" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "queryType": "traceql",
          "query": "{ resource.service.name = \"trustusbank-agentgw\" }",
          "limit": 25
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "table",
      "title": "Recent MCP-server traces (Tempo)",
      "gridPos": { "h": 10, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 18 },
      "datasource": { "type": "tempo", "uid": "tempo" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "queryType": "traceql",
          "query": "{ resource.service.name =~ \"account-mcp|transaction-mcp|ticket-mcp|currency-converter\" }",
          "limit": 25
        }
      ]
    },

    {
      "type": "logs",
      "title": "MCP-server stdout — last 30m",
      "gridPos": { "h": 10, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 28 },
      "datasource": { "type": "loki", "uid": "loki" },
      "options": { "showTime": true, "wrapLogMessage": true, "dedupStrategy": "none" },
      "targets": [
        { "expr": "{namespace=\"trustusbank-bank-mcp\"}", "refId": "A" }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "logs",
      "title": "ztunnel access log — last 30m (HBONE / deny verdicts)",
      "gridPos": { "h": 10, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 28 },
      "datasource": { "type": "loki", "uid": "loki" },
      "options": { "showTime": true, "wrapLogMessage": true, "dedupStrategy": "none" },
      "targets": [
        { "expr": "{namespace=\"istio-system\", app=\"ztunnel\"}", "refId": "A" }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
